### [Deuteronomy Chapter 1](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#001.md)

Overview

[Deu 1:1](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#001.md), Moses' speech in the end of
the fortieth year; [Deu 1:6](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#006.md), briefly
rehearsing the history of God's sending them from Horeb; [Deu
1:14](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#014.md), of giving them officers; [Deu
1:19](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#019.md), of sending the spies to search
the land; [Deu 1:34](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#034.md), of his anger for
their incredulity; [Deu 1:41](../../../bib/kjv/deu001.htm#041.md), and
disobedience.

